content:
Analyze Your Data

Find answers to business questions with Data Cloud reports. These examples illustrate how different industries can use Data Cloud reports to identify which customers or areas of business to focus on.

INDUSTRY	EXAMPLE	DATA CLOUD REPORT
Automotive	Identify customers due for service	Create a Vehicle Telematics DMO report, and bucket customers by mileage.
Automotive	Identify customers to recommend additional services to	Create a Vehicle Telematics DMO report, and group records by vehicle model and the latest signals from the vehicle.
Banking	Identify the top 1% of customers who performed high-value transactions last year and offer them a lower interest rate on loans	Create a Financial Account Transaction DMO report.
Cosmetics and Personal Care	Analyze customer browser behavior to optimize marketing strategies	Create a Product Browse Engagement DMO report.
Ecommerce	Analyze the performance of email marketing campaigns across countries	Create an Email Engagement DMO report.
Healthcare	Identify patients who need health check reminders	Create a calculated insight report on a unified patient profile, and group patients by age and health score.
Healthcare	Identify enrollees by program eligibility	Create a Care Program DMO report, and group enrollees by care program eligibility.
Healthcare	Identify patients who need reminders for follow-up visits after surgeries and hospitalizations	Create an Individual DMO report.
Healthcare	Optimize communication strategies based on patient consent data	Create a custom DMO report using the Engagement Channel Type DMO and Engagement Channel Type Consent DMO.
Hospitality	Provide discounts to active loyalty members based on their tier level	Create a Loyalty Program Member DMO report.
Insurance	Identify insurance policies due for renewal	Create an Insurance Policy DMO report, and bucket customers by policy renewal date.
Retail	Manage inventory levels efficiently based on sales data.Create a Sales Order Product DMO report.
Retail	Identify loyalty program members eligible for benefits	Create a custom report type that combines individual and loyalty program member DMOs.
Telecommunications	Improve case resolution speeds Create a Case DMO report.
title: Data Cloud Report Examples for Various Industries
